column3: The start of the game was delayed while players gathered around the plate. Baskets of flowers were presented to Mgr Rickey and Clarence Mueller. Mayor Kiel then tossed three wide ones to catcher Herman Bader and the game was on. In the stands were 150 Red rooters here from Cincinnati to see their pets play ball.FILENAME_TX"
